notes: schemaVersion 2.0-prices: Added items dict for priceKey-based lookups
All prices in CAD. cadToCoins defines conversion rate (1 CAD = 1000 coins).
Keys use a flat default price. Souvenir packages do not require keys.
marketFeePercent is applied to seller proceeds (credited = price * (1 - fee/100)).
tradeLockDays determines how long items are locked after acquisition.
rarityFallbackPrices used when specific item price not found in items dict.
wearMultipliers adjust base price by condition.
statTrakMultiplier multiplies price for StatTrak items (default 2.0).
lastBootRefreshAt: timestamp of last price refresh on VM boot
lastFullRefreshAt: timestamp of last full weekly price refresh
items dict populated by external price refresh script, not Lumia commands
